{"tid":1672400,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［先下手為強］今日係咩日子大家知唔知？","createTime":"2019-10-24T05:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T06:40:03.000Z","uid":73959,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ab3d56471fdd1cf89f102b6dbe2d0953bd359d17","tid":1672400,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"今日距離區選仲有啱啱有一個月<br />\n我知實有人話咩血債票償係食人血饅頭<br />\n但大家要認清楚事實<br />\n冇一個黨派係絕對好 (民建聯當然係絕對仆街）<br />\n但大是大非前<br />\n我哋唔可以忽略呢個選舉<br />\n<br />\n我估林鄭絕對有機會想將區選cancel或者延遲<br />\n而cancel原因係<span style=\"color: red;\">社會動盪以導致選舉不能夠安全舉行</span><br />\n所以我預計選舉前<span style=\"color: gold;\">一星期內</span>會有大型衝突發生<br />\n咁先可以fit到劇本<br />\n<br />\n為見及此<br />\n大家覺得好唔好做個宣言<br />\n示威者於選舉前三日(22,23,24)同後一日(for點票)<br />\n會暫緩所有示威活動？<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家認真、理性討論下</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外候選人名單confirm咗之後<br />\n愚見認為要整返個黃藍list<br />\n方便各位分辨人定鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後當然少不了最大對手建制派嘅政績啦<br />\n好似以下呢啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smLLquv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmLLquv.jpg&h=aad41914&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3D1Jgb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3D1Jgb.jpg&h=62c73537&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNTEuWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNTEuWb.jpg&h=0a78ed13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCBnsHS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCBnsHS.jpg&h=3ccc63e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家update咗之後可以瘋狂貼連儂牆<br />\n等公公婆婆有得欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de325db2fa7651ba00aa1c682369431f0eb44fd","tid":1672400,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br 